/20\">n</span><span class=\"absolute left-0 top-0 text-cap-dark-green\" style=\"opacity:0.15\">n</span></span><span class=\"relative inline-block\"><span class=\"text-cap-grey/20\">t</span><span class=\"absolute left-0 top-0 text-cap-dark-green\" style=\"opacity:0.15\">t</span></span><span class=\"relative inline-block\"><span class=\"text-cap-grey/20\">.</span><span class=\"absolute left-0 top-0 text-cap-dark-green\" style=\"opacity:0.15\">.</span></span></span></div></div></div></div><section class=\"relative w-full bg-cap-ink\"><div class=\"sticky top-0 h-screen w-full overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0\" style=\"opacity:0\"><img alt=\"Anciennes zones agricoles\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fdurabilite_1.webp&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fdurabilite_1.webp&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fdurabilite_1.webp&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fdurabilite_1.webp&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fdurabilite_1.webp&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fdurabilite_1.webp&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fdurabilite_1.webp&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fdurabilite_1.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fdurabilite_1.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-cap-ink/90 via-cap-ink/40 to-transparent \n                md:bg-gradient-to-r md:from-cap-ink/90 md:via-cap-ink/50 md:to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-6 font-sans text-xs font-medium tracking-widest text-white/70 \n                right-6 md:right-12\">Crédit photo © <!-- -->Cap Congo Agro Palm</div></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0\" style=\"opacity:0\"><img alt=\"Restauration de l&#x27;écosystème\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fdurabilite_2.webp&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fdurabilite_2.webp&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fdurabilite_2.webp&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fdurabilite_2.webp&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fdurabilite_2.webp&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fdurabilite_2.webp&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fdurabilite_2.webp&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fdurabilite_2.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fdurabilite_2.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-cap-ink/90 via-cap-ink/40 to-transparent \n                md:bg-gradient-to-l md:from-cap-ink/90 md:via-cap-ink/50 md:to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-6 font-sans text-xs font-medium tracking-widest text-white/70 \n                left-6 md:left-12\">Crédit photo © <!-- -->Cap Congo Agro Palm</div></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0\" style=\"opacity:0\"><img alt=\"Plantations de palmiers à grande échelle\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbundundu%2FBANANADEMOFIELD.webp&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbundundu%2FBANANADEMOFIELD.webp&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbundundu%2FBANANADEMOFIELD.webp&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbundundu%2FBANANADEMOFIELD.webp&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbundundu%2FBANANADEMOFIELD.webp&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbundundu%2FBANANADEMOFIELD.webp&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbundundu%2FBANANADEMOFIELD.webp&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbundundu%2FBANANADEMOFIELD.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbundundu%2FBANANADEMOFIELD.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-cap-ink/90 via-cap-ink/40 to-transparent \n                md:bg-gradient-to-r md:from-cap-ink/90 md:via-cap-ink/50 md:to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-6 font-sans text-xs font-medium tracking-widest text-white/70 \n                right-6 md:right-12\">Crédit photo © <!-- -->Cap Congo Agro Palm</div></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0\" style=\"opacity:0\"><img alt=\"Régénération végétale\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbundundu%2FDJI_20251112123547_0512_D.webp&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbundundu%2FDJI_20251112123547_0512_D.webp&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbundundu%2FDJI_20251112123547_0512_D.webp&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbundundu%2FDJI_20251112123547_0512_D.webp&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbundundu%2FDJI_20251112123547_0512_D.webp&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbundundu%2FDJI_20251112123547_0512_D.webp&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbundundu%2FDJI_20251112123547_0512_D.webp&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbundundu%2FDJI_20251112123547_0512_D.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fbundundu%2FDJI_20251112123547_0512_D.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-cap-ink/90 via-cap-ink/40 to-transparent \n                md:bg-gradient-to-l md:from-cap-ink/90 md:via-cap-ink/50 md:to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-6 font-sans text-xs font-medium tracking-widest text-white/70 \n                left-6 md:left-12\">Crédit photo © <!-- -->Cap Congo Agro Palm</div></div></div><div class=\"relative z-10 -mt-[100vh] w-full\"><div class=\"flex min-h-screen w-full items-end px-6 pb-24 md:items-center md:px-16 lg:px-24 \n              justify-start md:justify-start\"><div class=\"w-full max-w-2xl text-left\"><div class=\"mb-8 h-1 w-16 bg-cap-yellow \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"></div><h2 class=\"font-unbounded text-4xl font-bold uppercase leading-tight tracking-wide text-white drop-shadow-lg md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">Valorisation des Terres</h2><p class=\"mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg font-light leading-relaxed text-white/90 drop-shadow md:mt-8 md:text-2xl \n                  \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">En ce qui concerne la protection de la nature, les espaces que nous utilisons pour nos plantations sont principalement des anciennes zones agricoles exploitées par les communautés. Il s’agit d&#x27;espaces qui avaient déjà été déboisés auparavant pour les besoins des champs.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex min-h-screen w-full items-end px-6 pb-24 md:items-center md:px-16 lg:px-24 \n              justify-start md:justify-end\"><div class=\"w-full max-w-2xl text-left md:text-right\"><div class=\"mb-8 h-1 w-16 bg-cap-yellow md:ml-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"></div><h2 class=\"font-unbounded text-4xl font-bold uppercase leading-tight tracking-wide text-white drop-shadow-lg md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">Préservation de l&#x27;Écosystème</h2><p class=\"mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg font-light leading-relaxed text-white/90 drop-shadow md:mt-8 md:text-2xl \n                  md:ml-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">Certes, quelques arbres présents sur ces sites ont dû être coupés, mais cela n’a pas entraîné une destruction de l’écosystème, car nous mettons en place de fortes actions de restauration à travers nos plantations.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex min-h-screen w-full items-end px-6 pb-24 md:items-center md:px-16 lg:px-24 \n              justify-start md:justify-start\"><div class=\"w-full max-w-2xl text-left\"><div class=\"mb-8 h-1 w-16 bg-cap-yellow \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"></div><h2 class=\"font-unbounded text-4xl font-bold uppercase leading-tight tracking-wide text-white drop-shadow-lg md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">Plantations à Grande Échelle</h2><p class=\"mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg font-light leading-relaxed text-white/90 drop-shadow md:mt-8 md:text-2xl \n                  \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">Nous avons réalisé des plantations à grande échelle, notamment de palmiers et d’autres essences, qui ont aujourd’hui bien évolué. La végétation est redevenue verte et dense, ce qui contribue à l’enrichissement de l’environnement.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex min-h-screen w-full items-end px-6 pb-24 md:items-center md:px-16 lg:px-24 \n              justify-start md:justify-end\"><div class=\"w-full max-w-2xl text-left md:text-right\"><div class=\"mb-8 h-1 w-16 bg-cap-yellow md:ml-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"></div><h2 class=\"font-unbounded text-4xl font-bold uppercase leading-tight tracking-wide text-white drop-shadow-lg md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">Régénération Responsable</h2><p class=\"mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg font-light leading-relaxed text-white/90 drop-shadow md:mt-8 md:text-2xl \n                  md:ml-auto\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\">Ainsi, notre approche vise non seulement à utiliser ces espaces de manière responsable, mais également à participer activement à la régénération de la couverture végétale pour les générations futures.</p></div></div></div></section></main><section class=\"bg-background pt-10 font-sans md:pt-32\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-[min(100%,80rem)] px-4 sm:px-6\"><div class=\"relative z-10 -mb-20 md:-mb-24\"><div class=\"group relative h-[min(24rem,75vw)] overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-[0_24px_60px_-12px_rgba(29,29,27,0.25)] sm:h-[22rem] md:h-96\"><img alt=\"Champs — CAP Congo\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover opacity-90 transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-[1.03]\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 80rem\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmais.webp&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmais.webp&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmais.webp&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmais.webp&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmais.webp&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmais.webp&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmais.webp&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmais.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Fmais.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-cap-forest/90 via-cap-dark-green/70 to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 flex flex-col justify-center p-6 sm:p-12 md:p-16 lg:p-24\"><h2 class=\"max-w-2xl font-unbounded text-2xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight text-background sm:text-3xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl\">Produire local, nourrir durablement.</h2></div></div></div></div><div class=\"w-full\"><div class=\"rounded-t-3xl bg-cap-ink px-4 pb-12 pt-24 text-background sm:px-10 md:px-12 md:pb-16 md:pt-40\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-7xl\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 border-b border-background/15 pb-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16\"><div class=\"spac